This is the first map I've ever made. It's got all of the elements I learned about hammer put into the map. I'm sure it's not optimized well and it's probably got a million problems I don't even know are problems. All criticism is welcome and any information is helpful. :) (if ladders bother you please tell me why and how to fix the problem) 


(there's a bendy ladder that looks weird and I can't seem to fix.. maybe someone will notice :D)
